body.name: Dresser for Bedroom, Dresser with Large Side Pockets and Hooks, Tall Fabric 16 Drawers Dresser, Sturdy Steel Frame, Rounded Corner Wooden Top Dresser for Closet, Rustic Brown
features: Upgraded & Side Pockets & Hooks: Our side pocket & hooks of the bedroom dresser redefine convenience. The large Hanging side pocket are suitable for storing toys, cosmetics, baby products, and handicrafts. Hooks allow you to hang keys, scarves, bags and other items for easy access at any time.

Drawer Dresser Safe for Your Family: 16 deep folding drawers are roomy and provide endless organization possibilities. Comes with 2 sets of anti-tip accessories to ensure accident prevention. The wooden top with rounded corners and high-quality non-woven fabric is more suitable for families with children.

Sturdy and Durable Dresser: Our tall dresser drawers are made from eco-friendly MDF boards.The sturdy steel frame and waterproof wooden top provide stable support and ensure years of use, and the 4 adjustable plastic feet protect your floors from scratches and are also designed for uneven floors.

Multi-Function Dresser Organizer: The modern design storage large dresser cabinet with various colors fit different space in your house. Comes with clothing storage drawers that can be placed inside or outside the wardrobe. The waterproof wooden top also holds essentials such as lamps, clocks and photos.

Easy Assembly Excellent Service: The overall size of the fabric dresser is 37.8"L x 11.8"W x 57.1"H. All parts and installation procedures are packaged with clear instructions. Comes with 2 sets of installation tools. If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact us for a satisfactory answer. Just click "contact seller" to get satisfied solutions, no cumbersome returns.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Much bigger than I expected
reviews.reviewText: I have a couple of these style dressers and I really needed another. This variation looks taller than my others and it looks really nice. I really like black oak color I got and it looks nice as well as it makes the drawers look more flush with the dresser and it feels strong, it shouldn't sag with heavy usage.The dresser fits a lot of clothes and toys and it is very functionable. The dresser is a metal frame with fabric baskets. The top and faces of drawers are a wood-like material. Its a specific style and not the classic wooden clunky dresser. I personally recommend attaching this to the wall if you have little kids.My old complaint is the awkward baskets on the side. I don't love the look and I find them awkward to reach inside them.Other than that I higher recommend this dresser and I find it functional and looks nice too.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Awesome for organizing!
reviews.reviewText: I will start by saying that if you purchase this, plan to secure it to the wall! It is VERY easy to tip over if you have small children who like to climb! That being said, it is decently sturdy as long as you have it secured. It’s a 2 person lift because it’s decently weighted. I love that the drawers are those foldable kind, but the front of the drawers having the hard piece is wonderful because there is no bulge. I use it as a dresser so mine is loaded with clothes. It took about 1hr to assemble but mostly because you have to place the handles on yourself and that took the most time.
